<plot>A marriage is about to become bait to the tabloid gossip of Bollywood's hot on-screen pair, Shekahar (Aashish Chowdhary) and Jaya (Sheetal Malhar). Thus further agitating the already strained relationship between the star and his wife Sapna (Dia Mirza). To rekindle the marriage, Shekhar plans on taking Sapna on a surprise vacation to the newly renovated home on the outskirts of London. An argument triggered by Jaya's phone call leaves Sapna stranded in the middle of a highway. There she meets Raj (Dino Morea), a suave, comforting, charming kind of a guy who offers Sapna a ride, a ride which will change her life forever.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?283616</url></doc>
